   What is TUV Quality Verification?

   TUV® ([46]www.tuev.at) Verified Quality Management System is the rarest
   and strictest quality and engineering status in the wheel industry. HRE
   has been a leader in the wheel industry for more than 30 years. As a
   result of this, HRE is one of only very few wheel manufacturers
   worldwide to receive this quality verification.

   For more information, call an HRE specialist at (760) 598-1960 or
